PGVRBody.PGVRCell:
@ID

condition="@ID=='I20'"

This means, that if the current GEDCOM Record ID: ex. '0 @I20@' is I20, then it's TRUE


@fact

condition="@fact!='BIRT'"

This means, that if the current GEDCOM tag: ex. 'DEAT' is not 'BIRT, then it's TRUE


@desc

condition="@desc!=''"

This means, that if the current GEDCOM tag: ex. '1 EVEN Some text' has some text, then it's TRUE


@generation
